stories.text:
Is it possible to make a hundred accounts and make them upvote a post? Would those upvotes count?

HN has a fairly effective system to only allow downvotes by 500 reputation points. But it allows upvotes to everyone. So a Sybil attack for upvoting is possible.

Is it considered white-hat to try this myself?

[1] https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sybil_attack
